snippet.title: Mad Devils Motion Comic
snippet.description:
Mad Devils is a co-op, arcade shooter set in a twisted WWII setting. What does an Allied occult squad do when betrayed, killed and resurrected as demons?  Their job.  Coming 2021.
Steam:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/1439630/Mad_Devils/

www.maddevilsgame.com
